Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Margarita Roxas Elementary School in Sta. Ana, Manila, to Margarita Roxas De Ayala Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 796
An Act Changing the Name of the Margarita Roxas Elementary School in Sta. Ana, Manila, to Margarita Roxas De Ayala Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Margarita Roxas Elementary School in Sta. Ana, Manila, is hereby changed to the Margarita Roxas de Ayala Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
